manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Are you still carrying bulky luggage for travel? Our travel compression bag set is the go-to solution to solve all the hassle for storage when you are travelling or moving or swapping seasonal clothing in your wardrobe. Our travel bags organizer for luggage can create up to 80% valuable space for additional clothes, blankets, pillows & towels. It's time to say goodbye to cumbersome baggage. Simply pack all your belongings in your suitcase, briefcase, backpack or trolley with our space bags for an effortless packing experience. Our pack bag combo comes with 2 sized bags- Large and Medium, fitting all your need for packing a carry-on, luggage case and backpack during travelling and camping. The compression bags can also function as laundry bags and dry bags to store dirty clothes separately or keep swim gears dry.

Product Details Dual Zipper The dual zipper of our roll up bags makes sure that the bag is fully sealed and no air get back in. No Pump/Vacuum Needed No need to use a vacuum cleaner or a hand pump to suck air out. Simply roll the bag from one end to the other. Premium Material Our travel space bags are made from premium materials (PA + PE) to ensure strength and reliability, protecting your clothes from dirt and dust during travel and rainy seasons. Multi-Use Fits your need for packing a carry-on, luggage case and backpack during travelling and camping.

4-STEP Compression Packing Simply place your items into the packing bagSeal the zipperRoll the bag from the zipper to the bottom to get rid of all the airYour clothes will be reduced to its fractional size in a minute

Usage Tips Completely dry all items before storing them in travel compression packing bag.Avoid over-stuffing, use multiple bags instead.Double check the zippers for full closure, avoid items with sharp corners.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars You get what you pay for
reviews.reviewText: I wanted to love these so much more! These bags are a great size of large and fluffy comforters, pillows, duvets etc. there is a blue slide that is intended to help you seal the bag better, but they popped off easily while sliding and I had to go back over the double zip lock with my fingers because it wasn’t sealing with the blue tab.The bags came with a very handy hand pump that worked great but also took a LONG time to use for the size of the bags. But I didn’t mind because it got the job done for half the cost of other bags with electric pumps.I waited a week to write this review because I wanted to see how the bags held up. Sadly after 4 days two of the three used bags inflated back up completely. I chalked it up to my poor packing and re did it again. Sadly, they were puffed back up in only two days this time.I can’t be fully mad because you get what you pay for, but - I wouldn’t recommend these to anyone else. I’d keep looking and get the better quality bags.
